oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dental Emergency Equipment Inventory of Major Bernard Edwin Ragland
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Major Bernard Edwin Ragland (1894-1963) served in the Dentist Corps and was a member of the Medical Detachment of the 155 Inf. Regt., 39th Div. during World War I. This is an inventory of dental emergency equipment that Major Ragland had in his supply during or after the war.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: World War, 1914-1918; World War, 1914-1918 - History
